  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $2500 - $3200 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Changi Airfreight Centre</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Monday to Friday (9am to 6pm)</strong></li><li><strong>TRAINING PROVIDED</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Handle daily operations documentation like import and export permit, Air Waybills and Bill of Lading</strong></li><li><strong>Monitor import and export shipments</strong></li><li>Coordinate with internal teams and external partners to optimize logistics operations</li><li>Perform other assigned duties </li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess minimum GCE ‘N’ or ‘O’ level qualification </li><li><strong>Training provided for those lesser/without experience</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><ul><li>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</li><li>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</li><li>EA License No: 21C0492</li></ul>",
